<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Place new boot big band and small band onto differential side (or intermediate shaft side) boot so that band end (1) bends against forward rotating direction [a] as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Be sure to use new boot bands.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not squeeze or distort boot when fastening boot with boot bands. Squeezing boot to force air out may distort boot and reduce its durability.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
